t from border cafe. it has a nice atmosphere, with the wood work, funky artwork and opera music playing in the background, loud enough to hear but not be offensive. this is definitely a place to check out if you are in the area! don't be fooled by the exterior as i was.", "business_id": "GPhnm_rcjkbc_b96DVS5HQ", "stars": 4, "date": "2009-01-07", "type": "review"}